---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Our Story" description="About Weekend Basecamp">
  <Header slot="header" />

  <div style="max-width:760px;margin:4rem auto;padding:0 1.5rem;">
    <h1 style="font-size:2.5rem;font-weight:900;">Our Story</h1>
    <p style="font-size:1.1rem;line-height:1.8;color:#4a4a4a;">
      Weekend Basecamp started with a simple idea: every weekend is an opportunity to build a memory with the people you love most.
      We curate gear guides and outdoor tips so you can spend less time researching and more time making memories.
    </p>
  </div>

  <Footer slot="footer" />
</BaseLayout>
